You wake up in a big hall made of stone. There is some light coming from all directions.

After a life time, you still wondering the same old questions: "Why am I here?", "Where I came from?" and "What's my purpose?".

And now, you have created these rooms with your imagination, in order to search for those answers.  I'm convinced as well that in the items from here are answers that has been already found, hidden as meaningful and symbolic objects.  Yes, objects hidden in the deepest corners of your mind, waiting for being discovered or remembered.
